{"tid":1778461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錢錢錢 希望大家勇躍捐錢","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T03:50:55.000Z","uid":44559,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"810edb58e77ba1762e0f0e56f13b7746bcbf450d","tid":1778461,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"香港<br />\n1 仔女GEAR<br />\n2 仔女衣食住行 醫藥費<br />\n3 被捕仔女 法律支援<br />\n4 被捕仔女 生活開支<br />\n5 被捕仔女 家庭開支<br />\n<br />\n非香港<br />\n1 仔女衣食住行<br />\n2 仔女 中期生活安排: 搵工/讀書<br />\n3 仔女離開所需洗費<br />\n<br />\n全部都係錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好多時D人話香港人有既係錢，但其實好多捐錢既都唔係真係好有錢<br />\n好多都係節衣縮食節省番黎<br />\n<br />\n如果睇到呢個POST 既你，有錢有心希望多D捐錢 少D屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482ced7017ffa6fb2ba79dfce9658e13fa1aeaeb","tid":1778461,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"[行動]和你踩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2439b2ebaea318ace078ed6b4a02f03def08e20","tid":1778461,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22506a9f7b8b81fdc0798be49978b79b528dcc83","tid":1778461,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73b831013f031713dcf6b302eef82a29b45774c","tid":1778461,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b392d2c13c4c565c20ac11475754320b32d6e7","tid":1778461,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\"